# Any [[dense]], [[bready]] [[cake]], such as [[pound cake]] or [[teacake]], suitable for packaging and serving and consuming during a [[journey]].
types.html:
gâteau de voyage m (plural gâteaux de voyage)

  1. Any dense, bready cake, such as pound cake or teacake, suitable for packaging and serving and consuming during a journey.
trans: Any dense, bready cake, such as pound cake or teacake, suitable for packaging and serving and consuming during a journey.
